---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import FooterMain from "../components/FooterMain.astro";
import NavMain from "../components/NavMain.astro";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead
            title="Privacy Policy | Los Alamos Landscaping & More | Landscaping Services in NM"
            description="Learn how Los Alamos Landscaping & More collects, uses, and protects your personal information. Review our Privacy Policy for more details."
            keywords="Privacy Policy, Data Collection, User Information, Website Privacy"
            url="https://losalamoslandscaping.com/privacy-policy"
        />
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <NavMain />
        </header>
        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="padding-hero-xlbottom">
                    <div class="container-short">
                        <div class="wrapper">
                            <h1 class="title-page">Privacy <span class="text-red">Policy</span></h1>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 1. INTRODUCTION -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">1. Introduction</h2>
                        <p>
                            At Los Alamos Landscaping and More ("Company," "we," "our," or "us"), 
                            we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal information 
                            you provide to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, 
                            and safeguard your information when you visit our website at 
                            <a href="https://www.losalamoslandscaping.com">https://www.losalamoslandscaping.com</a> (the "Site").
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            By accessing or using the Site, you consent to the collection and use of your 
                            information as described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with any 
                            part of this policy, please discontinue use of our Site immediately.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 2. INFORMATION WE COLLECT -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">2. Information We Collect</h2>

                        <h3 class="title-sm text-red">2.1 Personal Information</h3>
                        <p>
                            When you use our Site, you may voluntarily provide us with personal information, including:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Full Name</li>
                            <li>Email Address</li>
                            <li>Phone Number</li>
                            <li>Address (if provided via contact forms)</li>
                            <li>Any additional information you provide when requesting services</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 class="title-sm text-red">2.2 Automatically Collected Data</h3>
                        <p>
                            When you visit the Site, we may automatically collect certain data, including:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Your IP Address</li>
                            <li>Device Type</li>
                            <li>Browser Type</li>
                            <li>Pages You Visit</li>
                            <li>Time Spent on the Site</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>This information is collected through cookies and analytics tools.</p>

                        <!-- 3. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                        <p>
                            We use the collected information for the following purposes:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
                            <li>To respond to inquiries and requests</li>
                            <li>To enhance the user experience</li>
                            <li>To analyze website traffic and usage patterns</li>
                            <li>To send updates or promotional messages (only with consent)</li>
                        </ul>

                        <!-- 4. COOKIES & TRACKING TECHNOLOGIES -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">4. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
                        <p>
                            We use cookies and tracking technologies to improve our Site and analyze user activity. 
                            You can disable cookies through your browser settings, but doing so may affect certain 
                            functionalities of the Site.
                        </p>

                        <h3 class="title-sm text-red">4.1 Google Analytics</h3>
                        <p>
                            We use Google Analytics to understand user behavior and improve our services. 
                            Google Analytics collects IP addresses, browser types, and time spent on the Site. 
                            To learn more, review <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google’s Privacy Policy</a>.
                        </p>

                        <h3 class="title-sm text-red">4.2 Facebook Pixel</h3>
                        <p>
                            We use Facebook Pixel to analyze ad performance and user engagement. You can opt out of 
                            Facebook tracking by adjusting your <a href="https://www.facebook.com/help/568137493302217" target="_blank">Facebook ad settings</a>.
                        </p>

                        <h3 class="title-sm text-red">4.3 Hotjar</h3>
                        <p>
                            We use <strong>Hotjar</strong> to better understand how users interact with our Site. Hotjar 
                            records sessions, click interactions, scroll behavior, and heatmaps to help us enhance 
                            usability and customer experience. Hotjar does not collect personally identifiable 
                            information. To learn more, visit <a href="https://www.hotjar.com/legal/policies/privacy/" target="_blank">Hotjar’s Privacy Policy</a>.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            If you do not wish to be tracked by Hotjar, you can opt out by following 
                            <a href="https://www.hotjar.com/privacy/do-not-track/" target="_blank">Hotjar's opt-out instructions</a>.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 5. SHARING YOUR INFORMATION -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">5. Sharing Your Information</h2>
                        <p>
                            We do not sell or rent your personal data. However, we may share your information with:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Service providers assisting with website operations</li>
                            <li>Third-party payment processors (for online payments)</li>
                            <li>Legal authorities if required by law</li>
                        </ul>

                        <!-- 6. DATA SECURITY -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">6. Data Security</h2>
                        <p>
                            We take reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, 
                            no website can guarantee 100% security, and you provide information at your own risk.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 7. YOUR RIGHTS & CHOICES -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">7. Your Rights & Choices</h2>
                        <p>
                            You have the following rights regarding your personal data:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Access: Request a copy of your stored information.</li>
                            <li>Correction: Request corrections to inaccurate data.</li>
                            <li>Deletion: Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal limitations).</li>
                            <li>Opt-Out: Unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <!-- 8. CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                        <p>
                            We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be 
                            posted on this page with an updated effective date.
                        </p>

                        <!-- 9. CONTACT US -->
                        <h2 class="title-md">9. Contact Us</h2>
                        <p>
                            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <strong>Los Alamos Landscaping and More</strong><br/>
                            2470 E Road, Suite A<br/>
                            Los Alamos, NM 87544<br/>
                            (505) 662-6234<br/>
                            <a href="mailto:contact@losalamoslandscaping.com">contact@losalamoslandscaping.com</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <FooterMain />
    </body>
</html>

